<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 03:11:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国通胀测试即将到来，亚洲股市走势缓慢；猕猴桃幻灯片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-28/</link><description>周三亚洲股市在美国本周公布的通胀数据之前表现谨慎，这可能会影响美联储宽松周期的时机，而在央行软化利率鹰派立场后，新西兰元大幅下跌。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 02:33:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国称北京和莫斯科应加强亚太协调</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-beijing-moscow-should-strengthen-coordination-asia-pacific-2024-02-28/</link><description>中国外交部周三表示，中俄应加强在亚太事务中的沟通协调，共同维护地区安全、稳定和发展。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 02:15:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-beijing-moscow-should-strengthen-coordination-asia-pacific-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>美联储谨慎态度胜过欧佩克+减产延期的言论，油价下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-eases-fed-caution-outweighs-talk-opec-cut-extensions-2024-02-28/</link><description>周三亚洲早盘油价下跌，因美国降息周期推迟的前景抵消了欧佩克+延长减产的言论带来的提振。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 01:45:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-eases-fed-caution-outweighs-talk-opec-cut-extensions-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾总统称中国海军在南海的存在“令人担忧”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-navys-presence-south-china-sea-is-worrisome-says-philippine-president-2024-02-28/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周三表示，中国海军在南海的存在“令人担忧”，但不会阻止菲律宾保卫其海洋领土和保护其渔民。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 00:48:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-navys-presence-south-china-sea-is-worrisome-says-philippine-president-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>碧桂园面临清算申请，中国房地产业遭受新打击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-country-garden-faces-winding-up-petition-failure-pay-2045-mln-loan-2024-02-28/</link><description>碧桂园控股周三表示，已向这家陷入困境的开发商提交清算申请，原因是其未支付价值 2.05 亿美元的贷款，这加剧了中国遭受流动性危机打击的房地产行业的困境。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 00:47:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-country-garden-faces-winding-up-petition-failure-pay-2045-mln-loan-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国敦促最大核国家谈判“不首先使用”条约</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-urges-un-define-roadmap-exempt-non-nuclear-states-nuclear-threat-state-2024-02-28/</link><description>中国外交部军控司表示，拥有最大核武库的国家应谈判签署互不首先使用核武器条约或就此发表政治声明。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 00:14:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-urges-un-define-roadmap-exempt-non-nuclear-states-nuclear-threat-state-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>兄弟姐妹帮助中国比亚迪在泰国电动汽车市场抢占先机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/siblings-help-chinas-byd-grab-early-lead-thai-ev-market-2024-02-27/</link><description>一年多前，比亚迪作为这家中国电动汽车制造商在泰国的唯一全国经销商推出后，Pratarnwong 和 Pratarnporn Phornprapha 兄弟姐妹被迫频繁撕毁商业计划，因为销量不断飙升。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 23:05:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/siblings-help-chinas-byd-grab-early-lead-thai-ev-market-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>应用材料公司收到美国证券交易委员会 (SEC) 关于向中国发货的传票</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/applied-materials-receives-subpoena-sec-china-shipments-2024-02-27/</link><description>半导体设备供应商应用材料公司在周二提交的文件中表示，该公司二月份收到美国证券交易委员会（SEC）发出的传票，要求提供与某些中国客户发货相关的信息。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 22:21:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/applied-materials-receives-subpoena-sec-china-shipments-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：全球货币焦点转向新西兰</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-02-27/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 21:51:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>美国参议员质疑拜登的也门战略，希望得到国会授权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/senior-us-senators-want-congress-authorize-strikes-against-houthis-2024-02-27/</link><description>美国民主党和共和党参议员周二质疑乔·拜登总统应对胡塞武装袭击商业航运的战略，并认为他应该寻求国会授权对也门组织持续采取军事行动。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 20:01:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/senior-us-senators-want-congress-authorize-strikes-against-houthis-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>ASM International 上半年营收稳定，GAA 和中国需求提振第四季度订单</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asm-international-sees-stable-revenues-first-quarter-2024-02-27/</link><description>半导体设备制造商 ASM International 周二预计 2024 年上半年收入稳定，部分原因是其环栅 (GAA) 芯片制造技术推动 2023 年第四季度订单增加。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 17:36:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asm-international-sees-stable-revenues-first-quarter-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲电动汽车制造商需要更密切的合作才能赶上中国——雷诺首席执行官</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/europe-ev-makers-need-closer-collaboration-catch-up-with-china-renault-ceo-2024-02-27/</link><description>雷诺老板卢卡·德梅奥周二表示，欧洲汽车制造商和能源供应商需要加强合作，以在电动汽车（EV）行业规模方面赶上中国。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 15:27:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/europe-ev-makers-need-closer-collaboration-catch-up-with-china-renault-ceo-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>美国对伊朗实施新制裁，针对指挥官和航运</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-hits-iran-with-new-sanctions-targeting-commanders-shipping-2024-02-27/</link><description>美国周二宣布实施制裁，目标是伊朗和胡塞武装指挥官以及一艘向中国企业运送价值超过 1 亿美元伊朗商品的船只。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 14:35:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-hits-iran-with-new-sanctions-targeting-commanders-shipping-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>英国财长与 Shein 主席就伦敦 IPO 进行会谈 - 消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-finance-minister-held-talks-with-shein-chair-about-london-ipo-source-2024-02-27/</link><description>英国政府消息人士告诉路透社，英国财政部长杰里米·亨特已与 Shein 执行主席唐纳德·唐进行了会谈，这家中国创办的快时尚连锁店渴望在伦敦上市。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 13:51:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-finance-minister-held-talks-with-shein-chair-about-london-ipo-source-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪展示了可以漂浮的SUV</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-shows-off-suv-that-can-also-float-2024-02-27/</link><description>中国比亚迪周二在日内瓦车展上展示了其阳王U8，这是一款豪华插电式混合动力SUV，能够在发生水事故时漂浮。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 13:26:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-shows-off-suv-that-can-also-float-2024-02-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>